(123, 2, '2015-12-07 03:16:05', '2015-12-07 03:16:05', '<h2 class="bigger">Brand new modern Villa close on Berawa Beach with great ROI potential</h2><p>Here is an opportunity to own a brand new architect designed and master built villa, on rare beachside land, opposite one of the best surfing beaches in Bali, at a very affordable price.</p><p>This stylish two bedroom home offers luxury lifestyle for live in and/or high ROI for holiday rental for its popular beach location.</p><p>The villa has parking for car and bike.</p><p>As you enter the property through the solid timber gate you immediately step into a luxurious garden area and entry foyer.</p><p>A breezeway then takes you up through the villa to gain access to the spacious bedrooms on one side, the lounge, living, dining on the other and the outdoor gardens, sun deck, pool and bale directly ahead of you.</p><p>The architecture is contemporary, however the living room has a high Balinese pitched roof, keeping some traditional aspects to the property.</p><p>The living room and dining area have large sliding doors that stack into an alcove. These open the living and dining area to the breezeway, the garden and sun deck, giving light, fresh air and adding to the already spacious indoor outdoor feel.</p><p>The sliding doors also give you the option to enclose and lock the area for security and keep the entire area cool as an air-conditioned space.</p><p>The bedrooms are large, with three meter high ceilings, quality A/C’s and walk-in robes. Both bedrooms have ensuites with stunning bathtubs.</p><p>The villa also boasts a gourmet kitchen with granite bench tops, a powder room, plus a laundry with its own drying area.</p><p>There is a beautiful ten-meter swimming pool, finished to western standard.</p><p>Located only a hundred meters from the beach, adjacent to the beautiful Berawa temple, this home cannot be built out.</p><p>There is a wide sealed road that takes you to all the popular restaurants in the area, the Canggu Deli and Supermarket, the Canggu Club and Waterpark just minutes away. Batu Belig Beach and Seminyak are a short drive in one direction and the famous Echo Beach the other direction.</p><p>It is rare to buy land with this proximity and what land is available is increasing in price almost monthly.</p><p>The villa is currently under construction and due for completion October 2016 and will come with a 30-year lease and an option to extend for another 15 years. It is selling for just US$295k.</p>', 'Villa Berawa', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'villa-berawa', '', '', '2015-12-16 03:41:34', '2015-12-16 03:41:34', '', 0, 'http://www.mybaliproperties.com/?p=123', 0, 'post', '', 0),
