(158, 2, '2015-12-08 07:31:27', '2015-12-08 07:31:27', '<h2 class="bigger">Brand New Modern Villa Close to Berawa Beach Potential for Great ROI</h2><p>Here is an opportunity to own a brand new architect designed and master built villa on rare beachside land opposite one of the best surf beaches in Bali, at a very affordable price.</p><p>This stylish 2 bedroom home offers luxury lifestyle for live in and / or high ROI for holiday rental for its popular beach location.</p><p>The villa is accessed via the garage which has parking for a car plus motorbikes.</p><p>As you enter the property through the solid timber gate you immediately step into a garden area and entry foyer.</p><p>A breezeway then takes you up through the villa to gain access to the spacious bedrooms on one side, the lounge , living , dining on the other and the outdoor gardens , sundeck , pool and bale directly ahead of you.</p><p>The architecture is contemporary, however the living room has a high timber Balinese pitched roof keeping some traditional aspects to the property.</p><p>The living room and dining area has large sliding doors that stack into an alcove and which opens the whole area up onto the breezeway , the garden and sundeck and the pool giving light , fresh air and adding to the already spacious living indoor outdoor area.</p><p>The sliding doors also give you the option to enclose and lock the area for security and keep the entire area cool in an air conditioned space.</p><p>The bedrooms are large with 3 metre high ceilings , airconditioners and walk in robes , both bedrooms have ensuites with stunning bathtubs.</p><p>The villa also boasts a gourmet kitchen with granite benchtops , a powder room , laundry and drying area , 10 metre pool and finishes to  high western standards.</p><p>Located only a hundred metres from the beach adjacent to the beautiful Berawa temple, this home cannot be built out.</p><p>There is a wide sealed road that takes you out to all the popular restaurants in the area , the Canggu Deli and Supermarket , the Canggu Club and Waterpark just minutes away.    Batu Belig Beach and Seminyak a short drive in one direction and the famous Echo Beach the other diretion.</p><p>It is rare to buy land with this proximity to the beach and is increasing in price every year</p><p>The villa is currently under construction and due for completion October 2016 and will come with a 30 year lease and an option to extend for another 15 years, with a sale price of  just US$295k / IDR 3.875.000.000.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Villa Berawa Beach', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '123-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-08 07:31:27', '2015-12-08 07:31:27', '', 123, 'http://www.mybaliproperties.com/123-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(159, 2, '2015-12-08 07:42:21', '2015-12-08 07:42:21', '<h2 class="bigger">Brand new modern Villa close to Berawa Beach with great potential for ROI</h2><p>Here is an opportunity to own a brand new architectually designed and master built villa, on rare beachside land, opposite one of the best surfing beaches in Bali, at a very affordable price.</p><p>This stylish 2 bedroom home offers luxury lifestyle for live in and/or high ROI for holiday rental for its popular beach location.</p><p>The villa has parking for cars plus motorbikes.</p><p>As you enter the property through the solid timber gate you immediately step into a luxurious garden area and entry foyer.</p><p>A breezeway then takes you up through the villa to gain access to the spacious bedrooms on one side, the lounge, living, dining on the other and the outdoor gardens, sundeck, pool and bale directly ahead of you.</p><p>The architecture is contemporary, however the living room has a high timber Balinese pitched roof, keeping some traditional aspects to the property.</p><p>The living room and dining area have large sliding doors that stack into an alcove. These open the living and dining area to the breezeway, the garden and sundeck, giving light, fresh air and adding to the already spacious indoor outdoor feel.</p><p>The sliding doors also give you the option to enclose and lock the area for security and keep the entire area cool as an air conditioned space.</p><p>The bedrooms are large with 3 metre high ceilings , air conditioners and walk-in robes. Both bedrooms have ensuites with stunning bathtubs.</p><p>The villa also boasts a gourmet kitchen with granite benchtops, a powder room, laundry and drying area and 10 metre pool, finished to high western standards.</p><p>Located only a hundred metres from the beach, adjacent to the beautiful Berawa temple, this home cannot be built out.</p><p>There is a wide sealed road that takes you out to all the popular restaurants in the area, the Canggu Deli and Supermarket, the Canggu Club and Waterpark just minutes away. Batu Belig Beach and Seminyak are a short drive in one direction and the famous Echo Beach the other direction.</p><p>It is rare to buy land with this proximity and what land is available is almost increasing monthly.</p><p>The villa is currently under construction and due for completion October 2016 and will come with a 30 year lease and an option to extend for another 15 years. It is selling for  just US$295k / IDR 3.875.000.000.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Villa Berawa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '123-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-08 07:42:21', '2015-12-08 07:42:21', '', 123, 'http://www.mybaliproperties.com/123-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
