(169, 2, '2015-12-14 16:39:10', '2015-12-14 16:39:10', '<h2 class="bigger">The Property: Villa Mutiara</h2><p>The Villa has been exquisitely designed as an incredible family home. It also has the ability to be an amazing rental property.</p><p>If you are looking for a family home then this is it! It''s situated on 11 are of Hak Malik (freehold) land surrounded by countryside on the top of the Bukit hillside. The house is 470 square meters under roof situated over three levels. It has a huge sun desk surrounding a large swimming pool. It has a skate board park, stunning gardens and a large triple garage. There are ocean views from the upper level and natural views of the surrounding countryside from the living area. This really is a rare opportunity to buy a home that has been built with love and designed to perfection.</p><h2 class="bigger">The Designer</h2><p>The Architect of this property is the existing owner. He has designed and built 5 family homes. This is his latest, with all of his experience and knowledge going into this property. Every one of his homes have sold quickly, with buyers lining up to purchase. He has a rare talent for design, especially for family homes.</p><h2 class="bigger">The Offer</h2><p>This is a freehold property based on 10.7 are of land in the prime residential area of Pecatu on the Bukit in Bali. The home has a build area of 770 sq meters. For this property the owner is wanting 13 billion rupiah. (US $940,000 approx.) There is a management company in place should you wish to put this beautiful property to work as a rental. If you are interested, we can get some projected returns to you.</p>', 'Villa Mutiara', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '133-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-14 16:39:10', '2015-12-14 16:39:10', '', 133, 'http://www.mybaliproperties.com/133-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
