(222, 2, '2015-12-17 06:26:54', '2015-12-17 06:26:54', '<h2 class="bigger">The Vision</h2><p>AQ~VA Hotel &amp; Villas is a tranquil condohotel that offers a mix of stylish housing from one and two-bedroom apartments to two-bedroom townhouses to three and four-bedroom villas.<br />Visit the AQ-VA Hotel &amp; Villas website <a href="http://www.aq-va.com" target="_blank">here</a></p><h2>The Location</h2><p>AQ~VA is strategically located in the heart of Legian, an area that is rich with entertainment, shopping and restaurants. This affordable development has been built to the highest standards by a reputable developer who has vast experience in building and managing professionally designed resorts, boasting a portfolio of some of the most successful projects on the island, including the first apartments in Bali and first condohotel in Indonesia. With AQ-VA’s unique style, central location and secure title, this truly is a unique investment opportunity.</p><h2>Don''t Wait!</h2><p>Right now you have the ability to purchase an apartment or villa in AQ~VA Hotel for a great price! As an owner of an AQ~VA apartment or villa you can use your property whenever you want, for as long as you want. You can even live in it if you so wished. But when you are not in residence you have the ability to place it into the hotel’s rental pool. It becomes part of the hotels room stock, being rented to paying guests by management. From the income derived you will receive 60%, and not have to do a thing for it! The only thing you have to do is inform management of when you would like to use your apartment or villa next.</p><h2>Finance Available</h2><p>The developer is offering extended payment plans or a guaranteed return on investment*</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>If you would like to find out more about this amazing offer please contact us!</p><p>* conditions apply</p>', 'AQ~VA Hotel - Apartments & Villas for Sale!', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '70-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-17 06:26:54', '