(227, 2, '2015-12-17 06:34:12', '2015-12-17 06:34:12', '<h2 class="bigger">The Vision</h2><p>To build a beautiful beach side property that offers investors a combination of an incredible family home with the added benefits of amazing rental potential.</p><h2 class="bigger">The Property: Villa Kemuning</h2><p>The Villa has been exquisitely designed to combine both aspects of The Vision, and comes fully furnished by one of Bali’s leading interior designers.</p><h2>The Developer</h2><p>The Developer has been in Bali for over 15 years, in which time he has been at the forefront of some of the most ground-breaking developments on the island. Listed on his incredible CV are;</p><p>• The Villas, which was the forerunner for all the villa developments here in Bali.<br /> • The Elysian, one of Bali’s most successful boutique hotels.<br /> • O-CE-N Hotel, the first beachfront condo-hotel in Indonesia.<br /> • His latest development Aramanis won two Australian Building Design awards.</p><p>What differentiates him from other developers is his extensive experience with luxury properties, cutting edge design skills and most importantly, his attention to detail.</p><h2>The Design</h2><p>The Architect of this property has over 15 years experience in the architecture and construction industries in both Southeast Asia and the United States. He has most recently completed 4 years in design and project management with the largest private developer in Singapore, Far East Organization, leading their luxury residential projects alongside world famous architects Arquitectonica, Fumihiko Maki, WOHA, and the influential Japanese design firm Super Potato. His experience, design skills and project management abilities are second to none here in Bali.</p><h2>The Offer</h2><p>We are offering you this exceptional property with a 40 year lease for only US $450,000 with the option of a guaranteed 6% return per annum for three years.</p>', 'Villa Kemuning', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '30-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-17 06:34:12', '2015-12-17 06:34:12', '', 30, 'http://www.mybaliproperties.com/30-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
